FBIS3-33053 "drlat033_r_94002" FBIS-LAT-94-033 Document Type:Daily Report 17 Feb 1994 Peru Fujimori To Confirm Bustamante Resignation PA1602192194 Lima Radio Programas del Peru Network in Spanish 1800 GMT 16 Feb 94 PA1602192194 Lima Radio Programas del Peru Network Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [From the "Newspaper of the Airwaves" newscast] [Text] President Alberto Fujimori will confirm in a few hours the resignation of Alfonso Bustamante y Bustamante as president of the Council of Ministers. Bustamante reportedly resigned on 10 February after the government decided to promulgate the law on the controversy over jurisdiction.
